### Demo accounts
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/demo-accounts

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Dashboard
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search tasks
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks?projectId=1&status=REVIEW
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
